QuestData.Title: The Search Continues
QuestData.Description: You thoroughly search this cluster of murloc hovels, and find no trace of the Menethil statuette.$B$BPerhaps one of the two nearby hovels to the north and northeast will have more clues.
QuestData.RewardText: This barrel is largely untouched. Prying it open...$B$B...you are assaulted by the pungent odor of cheese. It's a little wet, but still tasty!
